title: Asia - Live in Massachusetts '83 (m4a)
description:
Audience recording of Asia at the Centrum in Worcester, MA 8-22-83 during their "Alpha" tour. Only known live material from 1983 with John Wetton on vocals:

DISC 1:
Wildest Dreams
Time Again
The Heat Goes On
Eye To Eye
Only Time Will Tell
Keyboard Solo
Beginnings
Valley Of Rocks
The Clap
Midnight Sun

DISC 2:
Don't Cry
The Last To Know
Open Your Eyes
The Smile Has Left Your Eyes
Here Comes The Feeling
Drum Solo
Sole Survivor
Heat Of The Moment


Lineup:
John Wetton - lead vocals, bass guitar
Steve Howe - electric and acoustic guitars, vocals
Geoff Downes - keyboards, vocals
Carl Palmer - drums and percussion

Enjoy!
